oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." This is part one of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is the fifteenth of an unidentified number of tapes.
